@startuml ProjectPipeline_Flow
[*] --> Idea

Idea --> Planning : Evaluate & Accept
Idea --> Discarded : Reject
Planning --> Active : Start Project
Active --> OnHold : Pause
OnHold --> Active : Resume
Active --> Completed : Finish All Tasks
Completed --> Archived : Archive
Archived --> [*]

note right of Active
  Tasks in progress
  Resources being used
  Timeline tracking
end note

@enduml
